headline: Kimberly-Clark to Announce Third Quarter 2025 Results on October 30, 2025
summary: Kimberly-Clark (NASDAQ: KMB) will issue its third quarter 2025 results on Thursday, October 30. A press release and supplemental materials will be issued at approximately 6:30 a.m. EDT.
